00:00:24,260 --> 00:00:28,960
Today we're talking about a paper that connects 1842 cotton mills to the

8
00:00:28,960 --> 00:00:32,840
thing that's actually bottle-necking AI productivity right now.

9
00:00:34,060 --> 00:00:35,840
It's not what most people think.

10
00:00:36,880 --> 00:00:39,799
Set the scene, what happened when they added the third loom.

11
00:00:41,159 --> 00:00:45,960
Output per loom dropped, quality suffered, weavers couldn't keep up with

12
