18
00:01:13,400 --> 00:01:17,420
So the machine wasn't the bottleneck, the human watching the machine was.

19
00:01:18,819 --> 00:01:22,420
Exactly, and here's what happened over the next 60 years.

20
00:01:22,420 --> 00:01:28,379
By the early 1900s, a single weaver was managing 16 or more looms.

