00:03:35,099 --> 00:03:40,879
What clothes the gap? Three things, standardized verification procedures.

49
00:03:40,879 --> 00:03:45,879
Weavers learned systematic inspection patterns instead of ad hoc checking.

50
00:03:46,620 --> 00:03:51,020
Better tooling, improved thread tension indicators and early detection

51
00:03:51,020 --> 00:03:54,960
mechanisms that made problems visible before they became defects.

52
00:03:56,199 --> 00:04:01,419
And specialization, instead of one weaver doing everything, mills separated

53
